    "narrative": "The Austin Waves enter today\u2019s slate with a high-ceiling core, anchored by **Kyle Tucker** (77.26) and **Vladimir Guerrero Jr.** (75.26). **Kyle Tucker** earns our top spot despite a 42% rain risk; his favorable matchup against Roupp, combined with a wind-out factor and premium slotting at #2, makes him a foundational play. Similarly, **Vladimir Guerrero Jr.** benefits from a lucrative matchup against the struggling Kochanowicz (5.35 xERA). The wind at his back and a strong lineup placement ensure he remains our primary engine for counting stats today. **Luis Garc\u00eda Jr.** (73.66) and **Jackson Merrill** (70.92) also offer elite value, with **Luis Garc\u00eda Jr.** capitalizing on a dynamic platoon advantage against the high-xERA L\u00f3pez, while **Jackson Merrill** benefits from a massive 14% park factor boost.\n\nOur most difficult roster decision today involved the marginal threshold, where **Nolan Schanuel** (55.93) narrowly missed the final cut. While **Nolan Schanuel** provided a solid floor against the left-handed Corbin, he was pushed out by the higher efficiency scores of **Marcell Ozuna** and **Luis Robert Jr.**, who offer more substantial power-speed upside. We are keeping a close watch on **Heliot Ramos** (40.53); he sits right on the edge of our \"marginal\" tier and carries both a rain risk and a difficult matchup against Yamamoto. Should the weather turn or his lineup spot drop, he is the primary candidate to be pulled to preserve our game caps.\n\nBeyond the starters, we are exercising caution with **Gunnar Henderson** (55.74). While he remains in the lineup, his score is depressed by his matchup against the left-handed Bubic and an elite opposing hold rate that limits our stolen base opportunities in this specific contest. We are prioritizing efficiency over raw name value today to navigate the thin margins of our Roto standings, favoring the high-xERA matchups provided to **Nasim Nunez** and **Luis Garc\u00eda Jr.** to maximize our offensive production against targetable arms.",
